3 Signature calculation

This chunk calculates SBC gene signature Itâ€™s based on the idea of Univariate testing of Survival Data features NOTE: For now the rows where there is no censoring and time data will be removed from ALL datasets, until we find an imputation method.

The SBC signature on the dataset looks like this

  to_plot<-data.frame(Genes=signature.sbc)
